nodes.label: materiais_pedidos
nodes.query:
SELECT distinct sso.ID AS SERVICE_ORDER_ID, TO_CHAR(sso.CREATED_DATE,'DD/MM/RRRR HH24:MI:SS') AS DATA_CRIACAO, 
    TO_CHAR(eso.ISSUE_DATE,'DD/MM/RRRR HH24:MI:SS') AS DATA_FATURAMENTO,sso.STATUS AS STATUS_PEDIDO  ,st.NAME ,   
                   usuario.STRING_FIELD_VALUE AS usuario , 
                     empresa.STRING_FIELD_VALUE  AS cnpj,  st.ORGANIZATION , 
                   a.STATUS AS STATUS_STEP,  eso.SALES_ORDER_TYPE , eso.SALES_ORDER_NUMBER , eso.INVOICE_NUMBER AS fatura, 
                   eso.NF_NUMBER , stml.STATUS  AS STATUS_MATERIAL, smg.MATERIAL_GROUP ,  stml.MATERIAL_CODE , stml.DESC_MATERIAL ,  
                   stml.AMOUNT  AS QUANTIDADE_MATERIAL, stml.SERIAL_NUMBER, stml.external_plant_code CENTRO,
                stml.external_storage_location_code DEPOSITO  
              FROM   algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER sso , 
                     algarsom.SOM_TECHNICIAN_MATERIAL_LIST stml, 
                     algarsom.SOM_MATERIAL sm, 
                     algarsom.SOM_MATERIAL_GROUP smg, 
                     algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD usuario,  
                     algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD  empresa, 
                     algarsom.SOM_TECHNICIAN st , 
                     algarsom.SOM_EXTERNAL_SALES_ORDER eso,  
                     algarSOM.os_currentstep a ,  
                     algarSOM.SOM_workflow_instance i  
              WHERE sso.ID  = usuario.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID  
              AND   eso.ID = stml.FK_EXTERNAL_SALES_ORDER_ID   
              AND   stml.MATERIAL_CODE  = sm.COD_PRODUCT  
              AND   sm.FK_MATERIAL_GROUP  = smg.ID  
              and   usuario.FIELD_NAME  = 'DOCUMENT_NUMBER' 
              AND   sso.ID  = empresa.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID  
              and   empresa.FIELD_NAME  = 'ORGANIZATION_DOCUMENT' 
              AND   usuario.STRING_FIELD_VALUE = st.REGISTRATION   
              AND   stml.ID   = stml.FK_ROOT_TECH_MAT_LIST_ID  
              AND   sso.ID  = eso.FK_SERVICE_ORDER(+) 
              AND   a.entry_id(+) =  i.id_execution  
              AND   i.fk_service_order = sso.ID  
              AND   sso.FK_SERVICE_ORDER_TYPE  = 840 
              AND   eso.NF_NUMBER  IS NOT null 
              AND   sso.CREATED_DATE > to_date('31/12/2022','DD/MM/YYYY')

nodes.label: Pedidos em  Aberto
nodes.query:
SELECT sso.ID AS SERVICE_ORDER_ID,
       TO_CHAR(sso.CREATED_DATE, 'dd/mm/rrrr hh24:mi:ss') AS DATA_CRIACAO_PEDIDO,
       sso.STATUS,
       st.NAME AS NOME_TECNICO,
       usuario.STRING_FIELD_VALUE AS CPF_TECNICO,
       empresa.STRING_FIELD_VALUE AS cnpj,
       st.ORGANIZATION AS EMPRESA,
       (SELECT sp.EXTERNAL_PLANT_CODE 
		FROM   algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD ssof ,
		       algarsom.SOM_CONFIG_LINE_LOCATION scll , 
			   algarsom.SOM_PLANT sp 
		WHERE  scll.FK_ISSUE_PLANT_ID  = sp.ID 
		  AND  scll.ID = ssof.number_field_value
		  AND  ssof.field_name = 'SOM_CONFIG_LINE_LOCATION_ID'
		  AND  ssof.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID =  sso.ID) AS CENTRO,
	   ( SELECT ssof.STRING_FIELD_VALUE  
	     FROM algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD ssof 
	     WHERE ssof.FIELD_NAME  = 'EXTERNAL_STORAGE_LOCATION_CODE' 
	     AND ssof.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID  = sso.ID) AS DEPOSITO,
	   ( SELECT CASE ssof.STRING_FIELD_VALUE  WHEN 'ISSUE' THEN 'LIVRE'
	   										  WHEN 'REUSE' THEN 'REUSO'
	   										  WHEN 'INCIDENT' THEN 'INCIDENTE'
	   										  ELSE  ssof.STRING_FIELD_VALUE  END 
	     FROM algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD ssof 
	     WHERE ssof.FIELD_NAME  = 'STORAGE_TYPE'
	     AND ssof.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID  = SSO.ID) AS TIPO_DEPOSITO,
       a.STEP_NAME,
       depart.GERENTE,
       depart.COORDENADOR,
       depart.SUPERVISOR
  FROM algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER sso,
       algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD usuario,
       algarsom.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_FIELD empresa,
       algarsom.SOM_TECHNICIAN st,
       algarSOM.os_currentstep a,
       algarSOM.SOM_workflow_instance i,
       (SELECT scs.CUSTOMER         AS CPF_TECNICO,
               scs.COD_MATERIAL_SOM AS GERENTE,
               scs.COD_MATERIAL_SAP AS COORDENADOR,
               scs.DESC_MATERIAL    AS SUPERVISOR
               FROM algarsom.SOM_CARGA_SAP scs
               WHERE STATUS_OEBS= 'DEPARTAMENTAL') depart
 WHERE sso.ID = usuario.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID
   and usuario.FIELD_NAME = 'DOCUMENT_NUMBER'
   AND sso.ID = empresa.SOM_SERVICE_ORDER_ID
   and empresa.FIELD_NAME = 'ORGANIZATION_DOCUMENT'
   AND usuario.STRING_FIELD_VALUE = st.REGISTRATION
   AND usuario.STRING_FIELD_VALUE = depart.CPF_TECNICO(+)
   AND usuario.STRING_FIELD_VALUE <> 'ANONYMOUSUSER'
   AND a.entry_id(+) = i.id_execution
   AND i.fk_service_order = sso.ID
   AND a.STEP_NAME = 'Aprovação de Solicitação'
   AND sso.FK_SERVICE_ORDER_TYPE = 840
   AND sso.STATUS NOT IN ('CANCELADO', 'FECHADO')
 ORDER BY sso.CREATED_DATE

nodes.label: saldo materiais
nodes.query:
SELECT STML.ID,

STML.CPF,

(SELECT NX.NAME FROM ALGARSOM.SOM_TECHNICIAN NX WHERE REGISTRATION = STML.CPF AND ROWNUM=1) TECNICO,

(SELECT NX.ORGANIZATION FROM ALGARSOM.SOM_TECHNICIAN NX WHERE REGISTRATION = STML.CPF AND ROWNUM=1) ORGANIZATION,

(SELECT NX.ORGANIZATION_DOCUMENT FROM ALGARSOM.SOM_TECHNICIAN NX WHERE REGISTRATION = STML.CPF AND ROWNUM=1) ORGANIZATION_DOCUMENT,

smg.MATERIAL_GROUP,

STML.MATERIAL_CODE,

STML.DESC_MATERIAL,

STML.AMOUNT QUANTITY,

STML.SERIAL_NUMBER,

(SELECT to_char(tml.CREATED_AT,'dd/mm/rrrr hh24:mi:ss') FROM ALGARSOM.SOM_TECHNICIAN_MATERIAL_LIST tml WHERE tml.ID = STML.FK_ROOT_TECH_MAT_LIST_ID AND rownum = 1 ) AS DATA_CRIACAO,

seso.NF_NUMBER AS NOTA_FISCAL, seso.INVOICE_NUMBER FATURA, seso.sales_order_number NRO_OV

FROM ALGARSOM.SOM_TECHNICIAN_MATERIAL_LIST STML, ALGARSOM.SOM_EXTERNAL_SALES_ORDER seso, ALGARSOM.SOM_MATERIAL sm , ALGARSOM.SOM_MATERIAL_GROUP smg

WHERE STML.FK_EXTERNAL_SALES_ORDER_ID = seso.ID

AND stml.FK_MATERIAL_ID = sm.ID

AND sm.FK_MATERIAL_GROUP = smg.ID

AND STML.STATUS = 'DISPONIVEL'
